tags.name:
jwt-login
`a simple element to check for and fetch JWTs`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `jwt-login`
 * @customElement jwt-login
 * `a simple element to check for and fetch JWTs`
 * @demo demo/index.html
 * @microcopy - the mental model for this element
 * - jwt - a json web token which is an encrypted security token to talk
 */

attributes.name: body
attributes.description: Optional body, useful when doing posts

attributes.name: key
attributes.description: Key that contains the token in local storage

attributes.name: jwt
attributes.description: JSON Web token to securely pass around

properties.name: body
properties.description: Optional body, useful when doing posts

properties.name: key
properties.description: Key that contains the token in local storage

properties.name: jwt
properties.description: JSON Web token to securely pass around
